          <p class="text-[var(--drivon-muted)] mb-6">Our customer service team is here to help with any questions about our driver merchandise</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/contact" class="bg-red-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors font-medium">
              Contact Support
            </a>
            <a href="/collections" class="bg-gray-200 text-gray-800 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-300 transition-colors font-medium">
              Browse Collections
